TR_YOU_ARE_OPENING_TREZOR_BETA_WALLET.source: You are opening Trezor Beta Wallet

TR_TREZOR_BETA_WALLET_IS.source: {trezorBetaWallet} is a public feature-testing version of the {trezorWallet}, offering the newest features before they are available to the general public.

TR_IN_CONTRAST_COMMA_TREZOR.source: In contrast, {trezorWallet} is feature-conservative, making sure that its functionality is maximally reliable and dependable for the general public.

TR_PLEASE_NOTE_THAT_THE_TREZOR.source: Please note that the {trezorBetaWallet} might be collecting anonymized usage data, especially error logs, for development purposes. The {trezorWallet} does not log any data.

TR_TREZOR_WALLET_IS_AN_EASY_DASH.source: Trezor Wallet is an easy-to-use interface for your Trezor. Trezor Wallet allows you to easily control your funds, manage your balance and initiate transfers.

TR_THE_PRIVATE_BANK_IN_YOUR_HANDS.source: The private bank in your hands.

TR_DEVICE_NOT_RECOGNIZED_TRY_INSTALLING.source: Device not recognized? Try installing the {link}.
